# {{ project_name | pascal }} - Azure Event Hubs Producer

Auto-generated Go producer for Azure Event Hubs with CloudEvents structured and binary content modes.

## Quick start

```go
producer, err := {{ project_name | snake }}.New{{ class_name }}(
    "Endpoint=sb://...;SharedAccessKeyName=...;SharedAccessKey=...",
    "event-hub-name",
)
if err != nil {
    panic(err)
}
defer producer.Close(context.Background())
```

Use `New{{ class_name }}WithSender` to unit-test with a fake sender. Binary CloudEvents use Event Hubs application properties with the `cloudEvents:` prefix; structured CloudEvents use `application/cloudevents+json` as `EventData.ContentType`.

## Dependencies

- `github.com/Azure/azure-sdk-for-go/sdk/messaging/azeventhubs`
- `github.com/cloudevents/sdk-go/v2`
- `github.com/google/uuid`
